        "text": "Here at The Syllabus we feel the weight of history. After 100 editions, we will soon be publishing our 100,000th piece – our [https://cabinet.the-syllabus.com/archive/?size=n_30_n archive] reflects some tectonic changes in the topics we track. So, to celebrate these milestones, we’re dusting off our stacks, and looking back on two years of curated syllabi.\n"
